                Deo Mart<supplied reason="lost">i</supplied> <lb n="2"/>Enemn<supplied reason="lost">o</supplied><lb break="no" n="3"/>genus a<lb break="no" n="4"/>ram pos<lb break="no" n="5"/>uit vo<supplied reason="lost">t</supplied><lb break="no" n="6"/>um <lb n="7"/>solv<lb break="no" n="8"/>it pro se </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> et su<lb break="no" n="2"/>is <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>erito</ex></expan>
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Die Worte &amp;quot;&amp;quot;et su/is m(erito)&amp;quot;&amp;quot; sind am Ende der Z. 6-7 &amp;quot;&amp;quot;um / solv&amp;quot;&amp;quot; eingebaut. (B): Zu den leichten Leseabweichungen s. RIB 0742.</p>
            </div>
